title: #150: Nicholas Cage Is A Time Traveling Shaman with Gareth Reynolds.
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from the Dollop, Gareth Reynolds, to discuss whether Nicholas Cage is a time traveling shaman who uses his movies to warn us of the evils of the power elites!!!
Please check out my two new specials Armogeddon and Zero Fucks on Vimeo.com!
